# Drop your district's CA certificate here as ``ca.crt`` (PEM-encoded).
#
# It appears inside the backend container at
# ``/etc/paperclip/certs/ca.crt`` (read-only). Reference that path
# from ``PAPERCLIP_LDAP_CA_CERT_PATH`` in docker-compose.yml or your
# .env file.
#
# This file (.gitkeep) only exists so Git tracks the empty directory;
# it has no runtime effect.
